OL,6,FA former primary school teacher has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for sexual offences he
OL,8,Fcommitted against two pupils at the
OL,9,Fschool where he taught.
OL,11,FWilliam Maher from Kings Brae in
OL,12,FBelfast sat with his head bowed,
OL,13,Flistening to the mother of one of his
OL,14,Ftwo victims tell the court how his
OL,15,Foffending had devastated their family,
OL,16,Fan impact statement the judge
OL,17,Fdescribed as "powerful".
OL,19,FBefore sentencing, the mothers of both
OL,20,Fvictims had spoken anonymously to UTV
OL,21,Fto protect their children's identities.
