OL,6,FThe mothers were critical of how the
OL,7,FEducation Authority handled concerns
OL,8,Fover Maher's behavior before his first
OL,9,Fconvictions.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the Education
OL,12,FAuthority said: "Following today's
OL,13,Fsentencing, our thoughts are with the
OL,14,Fvictims and their families at this
OL,15,Fdifficult time.
OL,17,F"The safety and wellbeing of all
OL,18,Fpupils remains the EA's highest
OL,19,Fpriority and we treat all safeguarding
OL,20,Fmatters with the utmost seriousness.
